	<h1 class="title">音乐版权升值太快，索尼收回了音乐出版公司的股权</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/495481/small/495481.jpg?1456747733" alt="">
